text: Badreddine Benachour (born 2 July 1994) is a Moroccan footballer currently playing for Botola side Wydad Casablanca as a goalkeeper. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan footballers Category:Wydad AC footballers Category:Botola players Category:Sportspeople from Casablanca Category:Association football goalkeepers
